<subSubSection id="063C3A333A5D13C58A9597B93F0D02C1" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" type="description">
<paragraph id="9373A1E777A6E50FD5D88B5EF78CF434" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">Culture characteristics.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="28598B6B221FFE2296A8018D032B7909" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">Colonies on PDA, reached 3 cm diam. after one week at 25 °C, white, cottony, flat, low, dense, with slightly wavy margin; fructifications were not observed in culture.</paragraph>
